subject: From the office Vice Preside
body:
From the office Vice President of the United States
1800 G Street NW., Washington, DC 20502
https:/ /usun.usmission.gov/our-leaders/vice-president/
Attention: Dear
From the records of outstanding beneficiaries due to payment with the Federal Government of  United States of America (U.S.A) your email address was discovered as next on the list out of the 11 outstanding beneficiaries who have not yet received their payments during the tenure of the previous administration office.
Please bear with us for making this initial contact through email. You are required to fill and send this information for verification purpose only so that your fund valued at $9,500,000 will be remitted into your nominated bank account or delivered to you via atm card.
Your full name:
Mobile Number:
Home Address
Picture ID:
You are to reply to this email as soon as possible and we appreciate your soonest response as we apologize for any inconveniences this delay might put you through. reply to 
kamaladharriss655@gmail.com
Yours in service,
Kamala Harris
the Vice President of the United States of America

subject: Re:   From the office Vice Preside
body:
Dear Vice President Kamala Harris,

Thank you for reaching out to me regarding the payment with the Federal Government of the United States. I appreciate your efforts in contacting me through email. I would be happy to provide the necessary information for the remittance of my funds.

Could you please clarify what specific information you require from me? Additionally, could you explain the process of how my funds will be remitted into my nominated bank account or delivered via an ATM card?

I look forward to your prompt response and appreciate your assistance in this matter.

Best wishes,
Leo
